Production

docker compose -f docker-compose.yml -f docker-compose.prod.yml up --build -d
docker compose -f docker-compose.yml -f docker-compose.prod.yml down

Development

docker compose up --build -d (equivalent: docker compose -f docker-compose.yml -f docker-compose.override.yml up --build -d)
docker compose  down (equivalent: docker compose -f docker-compose.yml -f docker-compose.override.yml down)  


Seeding the datbaase

cd services/auth;
python seed_db; (run twice: first with BUSINESS_START_ID = 100; then BUSINESS_START_ID = 500)
python seed_materials;
python seed_locations;
python seed_transportations;


update database

alembic revision --autogenerate -m "create threads"
alembic upgrade head
alembic stamp 3f4915efc9a5